OL,3,C'I want to be proud': Why I'm finally
OL,4,Cshowing the world my scars
OL,6,FAda shared her story with ITV Granada
OL,7,FReports journalist Lauren Ostridge.
OL,9,FA beauty therapist who spent years
OL,10,Fhiding the scars on her chest and neck
OL,11,Fis now celebrating them on a national
OL,12,Fstage after her portrait made the
OL,13,Ffinals of a prestigious art
OL,14,Fcompetition.
OL,16,FFor years, Ada Osigwe says she felt
OL,17,Fashamed and embarrassed of her keloid
OL,18,Fscars, carefully choosing clothing to
OL,19,Fhide her visible difference and avoid
OL,20,Fany conversation about them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
