CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777464668
OL,3,C'I want to be proud': Why I'm finally
OL,4,Cshowing the world my scars
OL,6,FBut now her portrait, which
OL,7,Fprominently features her scars, has
OL,8,Fbeen selected as a finalist for the
OL,9,FRoyal Society of Portrait Painters in
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,FAda says the recognition marks a
OL,13,Fturning point for the Manchester-based
OL,14,Fbusinesswoman, who is now using her
OL,15,Fplatform to raise awareness about
OL,16,Fkeloids and the impact it can have on
OL,17,Fmental health and body image.
OL,19,FWhat is a keloid scar?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
