OL,3,C'I want to be proud': Why I'm finally
OL,4,Cshowing the world my scars
OL,6,FAda's scars formed when she was a
OL,7,Fteenager after undergoing surgery to
OL,8,Fher thyroid.
OL,10,F"For so many years, it was something
OL,11,FI've shied away from or avoided
OL,12,Ftalking about", she said. "I think
OL,13,Fit's because I wasn't accepting of it."
OL,15,F"I've allowed it to limit how I show
OL,16,Fup day-to-day; meeting new people,
OL,17,Fsituations that I walk into. I was
OL,18,Fconstantly angst about it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
