CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777464668
OL,3,C'I want to be proud': Why I'm finally
OL,4,Cshowing the world my scars
OL,6,FAda, who has undergone several types
OL,7,Fof treatments to minimise the
OL,8,Fappearance of the scars, has now been
OL,9,Ftold by doctors that there is nothing
OL,10,Fmore they can do.
OL,12,FBut now Ada has turned what she always
OL,13,Fthought was her weakness into her
OL,14,Fstrength to raise awareness of keloid
OL,15,Fscars in hope of helping others.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
