PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777464668
OL,3,C'I want to be proud': Why I'm finally
OL,4,Cshowing the world my scars
OL,6,FAda has started to documented her
OL,7,Fjourney on social media, and released
OL,8,Fher documentary about her life, and
OL,9,Fsays she is steadily building a
OL,10,Fcommunity of people who all live with
OL,11,Fkeloid scars.
OL,13,FAre there any treatment options for
OL,14,Fkeloid scars?
OL,16,FAccording to the NHS and British Skin
OL,17,FFoundation, keloids can treated to
OL,18,Freduce their size, flatten them, and
OL,19,Falleviate symptoms like itching and
OL,20,Fpain, though they cannot be completely
OL,21,Fcured and often recur.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
