OL,3,C'I want to be proud': Why I'm finally
OL,4,Cshowing the world my scars
OL,6,FTreatment methods include:
OL,8,F"I want to be proud and send the
OL,9,Fmessage out there. Regardless of
OL,10,Fwhatever skin visibility that you do
OL,11,Fhave, self acceptance and self love is
OL,12,Fso important. We need to that and get
OL,13,Fthat message out there."
OL,15,FInspired by her story, Manchester-
OL,16,Fbased fine artist Dylan Lisle asked
OL,17,FAda if he could paint her portrait
OL,18,Fwhich has now reached the final of the
OL,19,FRoyal Society of Portrait Painters in
OL,20,FMall Gallery in London.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
