PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777464668
OL,3,C'I want to be proud': Why I'm finally
OL,4,Cshowing the world my scars
OL,6,FShe said: "There's people out there
OL,7,Fwho are fighting a silent battle that
OL,8,Fwe will never know.
OL,10,F"I have shied away from so many things
OL,11,Fand opportunities and I felt like this
OL,12,Fwas one that I couldn't shy away from.
OL,13,FIt's such a strong story to put out
OL,14,Fthere."
OL,16,FAda's portrait will be featured in the
OL,17,FRoyal Society of Portrait Painters
OL,18,Fannual exhibition at London's Mall
OL,19,FGalleries from 7`19 May, with the
OL,20,Fwinner set to be announced prior to
OL,21,Fthe opening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
